-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（一）使用国家和省明令淘汰的用能产品、设备和生产工艺的；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（二）用能产品、设备不符合强制性能源效率标准的；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（三）单位产品能耗超过国家、行业或者地方限额标准的；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（四）不符合国家和省其他节能规定的。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">二、无第一条所述情形之一的投资项目：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（一）项目万元工业增加值能耗不高于浙江省2015年万元工业增加值能耗控制指标的，予以审批通过（年耗能5000吨标准煤以下）或转报省经信委（年耗能5000吨标准煤以上）。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（二）项目万元工业增加值能耗虽高于浙江省2015年万元工业增加值能耗控制指标，但低于湖北省2015年万元工业增加值能耗控制指标，年耗能5000吨以下项目予以审批通过；年耗能5000吨以上项目，在明确承诺淘汰项目所在区域相应落后产能进行用能等量或减量置换，或项目所在企业通过对原有产能实施节能改造实现节能量冲抵部分能耗，有效降低新上项目单耗，予以转报省经信委审批。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（三）对于万元工业增加值能耗高于湖北省2015年万元工业增加值能耗控制指标，但对区域经济有重大影响的龙头骨干项目或产业链补链项目，由项目所在区域政府、开发区（园区）管委会或项目业主承诺通过同步淘汰落后产能方式确保达到万元工业增加值能耗低于浙江省2015年控制指标的，经市政府同意后，予以审批通过（年耗能5000吨标准煤以下）或转报省经信委（年耗能5000吨标准煤以上）。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（四）其他达不到相应标准和要求的项目，节能审查不予通过或不予转报省经信委。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">三、浙江省2015年万元工业增加值能耗控制指标为0.8吨标准煤。湖北省2015年万元工业增加值能耗控制指标为 1.84吨标准煤。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">四、各县（市、区）可参照本标准制定本地节能审查标准。</span></p><p><br style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-ALIGN: left; FONT: 16px/30px Simsun; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" clear=\"all\"/></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">附件5</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">千吨标煤折（换）算方法</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">一、常用能源折算方法</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（一）电力：本《办法》所涉及电力能耗折算，除计算单位产品能耗外，均采用等价值方法换算，折算系数为：1000tce＝320万千瓦时。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（二）天然气：1000tce＝82.35万立方米。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（三）饱和蒸汽：1000tce＝11100吨。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（四）过热蒸汽：1000tce＝10000吨。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（五）柴油：1000tce＝578.5吨。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">（六）汽（煤）油：1000tce＝617.8吨。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">二、建筑领域换算方法</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">本《办法》所涉及千吨标煤建筑规模，具体换算方式如下：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 10.5pt/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px;