KGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">各县（市、区）人民政府，市政府各部门、直属各单位：&nbsp;<br/>　　根据《浙江省人民政府办公厅关于进一步加强行政审批中介服务管理的意见》（浙政办发〔2013〕136号）、《市委办公室市政府办公室关于全面深化行政审批制度改革工作的意见》（衢委办发〔2014〕9号）要求，为进一步加强对行政审批中介服务事项规范管理，经市政府同意，现将《湖北省行政审批中介服务事项办理时限和收费标准》予以公布，请遵照执行。&nbsp;<br/>　　一、列入《湖北省行政审批中介服务事项办理时限和收费标准》的中介服务事项，由行政审批申请人自行选择中介服务机构，行政机关不得指定中介服务机构。&nbsp;<br/>　　二、未列入《湖北省行政审批中介服务事项办理时限和收费标准》的，行政机关不得擅自将有偿中介服务事项作为行政审批事项的审批要件。&nbsp;<br/>　　三、实施服务承诺公开制度。中介服务机构要严格按照政府价格主管部门制定的收费管理规定执行，在收费场所醒目位置，通过价目表、价目册、价目牌、电子显示屏等方式将办理时限、收费项目、服务内容、计费单位、收费标准、收费依据以及12358价格举报电话等内容进行公示，接受社会监督。&nbsp;<br/>　　四、各中介机构行业主管部门以及相关部门要加强对中介服务机构的办理时限、收费情况、优质服务情况等进行指导、监督、考核。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: right; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/30px Simsun; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 32px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　湖北省人民政府办公室&nbsp;<br/>　　2014年7月16日</span></p><p><br/></p><p>					 	</p>', '2015-12-30 15:12:53', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 15:12:53', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 15:15:35', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
INSERT INTO `info_tcontent` VALUES ('402881fd515b4f9b01515b78e8be0013', '公共场所卫生管理条例实施细则', '', '超级管理员', '超级管理员', '', '<p>								</p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 38px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">卫生部令第</span></strong><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 43px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 38px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">号</span></strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: black; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 38px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">公共场所卫生管理条例实施细则</span></strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">第一章　总　则</span></strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第一条　根据国务院１９８７年４月１日发布的《公共场所卫生管理条例》（以下简称《条例》）特制定本实施细则。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第二条　各级卫生行政部门和国务院各部、委、局卫生职能部门要加强对卫生防疫机构的领导，健全机构，充实公共场所卫生技术装备和人员。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第三条　各级政府卫生行政部门所属的卫生防疫机构对管辖范围内的公共场所实施卫生监督。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　国境口岸及入出境交通工具的卫生监督按照《中华人民共和国国境卫生检疫法》及其实施细则的规定执行。民航、铁路、交通、厂（场）矿所属的卫生防疫机构负责对管辖范围内的机场、车站、码头等候室等公共场所和国内民航客机、铁路客车、客轮以及主要为本系统职工服务的公共场所实施卫生监督，并接受所在地地、市以上卫生防疫机构的业务指导，其主要对本系统外营业的公共场所以及尚无卫生防疫机构进行监督的单位由地方卫生防疫机构实施卫生监督。部队、学校以及其他系统所属的对社会开放的公共场所由所在地卫生防疫机构实施卫生监督。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">第二章　卫生管理</span></strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第四条　卫生防疫机构负责监督和指导公共场所经营单位对其从业人员进行卫生知识培训和考核工作，其中个体经营者的培训考核工作由所在地区卫生防疫机构负责。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　培训的具体要求：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）卫生防疫机构按全国“公共场所从业人员卫生知识培训教学大纲”编写教材；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）公共场所卫生负责人和从业人员必须完成教学大纲规定的培训学时，掌握教学大纲规定的有关卫生法规、基本卫生知识和基本卫生操作技能等；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）卫生防疫机构对受训人员的培训进行监督审核，对合格者在“健康合格证”上加盖考核合格章。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　新参加工作的从业人员应取得卫生知识合格证明后方可上岗工作；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）从业人员每两年复训１次。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第五条　公共场所从业人员健康检查的规定：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）旅店业、咖啡馆、酒吧、茶座、公共浴室、理发店、美容店、游泳场（馆）直接为顾客服务的从业人员（包括临时工，下同）每年进行１次健康检查，其它场所直接为顾客服务的从业人员每两年进行１次健康检查，取得“健康合格证”后方可继续上岗工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　新参加工作的人员上岗前须取得“健康合格证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　公共场所内经营食品的从业人员的健康检查按《食品卫生法》有关规定执行。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　可疑传染病患者须随时进行健康检查，明确诊断。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）公共场所主管部门负责健康检查的组织安排和督促检查工作。经营单位每年向所在地卫生防疫机构提交应进行健康检查的人员名单，并根据健康检查的结果，对患有《条例》第七条规定的疾病和其它传染性疾病者应调离其直接为顾客服务的工作岗位。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）各级卫生行政部门指定医疗卫生单位承担健康检查工作。健康检查应统一要求，统一标准，认真记录，建立档案。医疗卫生单位在健康检查两周内应向受检单位发出健康检查结果报告，合格者由卫生防疫机构发给“健康合格证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）“健康合格证”不得涂改、转让、倒卖、伪造。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（五）健康检查项目按卫生部颁发的有关预防性体检管理办法执行。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第六条　患有《条例》第七条规定的疾病卫生管理标准：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）病毒性肝炎　肝炎患者经系统治疗后基本痊愈（主要症状消失，肝区无明显压痛及肿大，肝功能正常，乙型肝炎表面抗原阴性）可恢复原工作。乙肝患者肝功能恢复正常，但乙型肝炎表面抗原阳性，需经六个月观察无恶化，可恢复原工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　乙肝病毒携带者若ｅ抗原阳性，不得从事理发美容业、公共浴室业直接为顾客服务的工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）痢疾（包括阿米巴痢疾、细菌性痢疾）经治疗临床症状和体征消失，大便培养阴性，停药后两周内大便培养３次阴性者，可恢复原工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）伤寒　临床症状和体征消失，大便连续培养３次阴性者可从事不直接为顾客服务的工作。经卫生防疫机构进行观察，第２年粪便检查连续进行两次培养阴性者，方可从事直接为顾客服务的工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）活动期肺结核　活动期肺结核和痰带菌者应隔离治疗，痰培养阴性或一周内连续痰涂片两次阴性，达到临床治愈方可恢复原工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（五）皮肤病　化脓性皮肤病、渗出性皮肤病及接触性传染的皮肤病患者治愈前不得从事直接为顾客服务的工作，治愈后方可恢复原工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（六）其它有碍公共卫生的疾病（重症沙眼、急性出血性结膜炎、性病等）需治愈后方可从事原工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第七条　“卫生许可证”发放管理规定：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）“卫生许可证”由县以上卫生行政部门签发，由各级卫生防疫机构负责发放管理。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　民航、铁路、交通、厂（场）矿卫生职能部门负责对管辖范围内的机场、车站、码头等候室等公共场所和国内民航客机、铁路客车、客轮以及主要为本系统职工服务的公共场所“卫生许可证”的发放工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）经卫生防疫机构进行审查监测确定主要卫生指标符合卫生要求，８０％以上直接为顾客服务的从业人员卫生知识培训合格的经营单位方可取得“卫生许可证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）对经营多种公共场所的单位只发放１个“卫生许可证”，并注明其兼营项目。因违法而需注销其中某个经营项目时，在“卫生许可证”的相应处加盖注销章，被注销经营项目的单位经卫生监督监测认定合格后，可申请恢复被注销的经营项目，并换发新证。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）“卫生许可证”发放程序：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　１．申领“卫生许可证”的单位到所属卫生防疫机构领取并填写“公共场所卫生许可证申请书”，经主管部门审核后送卫生防疫机构。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　２．卫生防疫机构委派卫生监督员按卫生标准和要求进行审查和监测，对符合要求的发给由卫生行政部门签发的“卫生许可证”。对审查、监测的资料应存档备查。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（五）新建、扩建、改建公共场所或变更营业项目的应按上述程序申领“卫生许可证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（六）“卫生许可证”每两年复核１次。复核时，经营单位应填写复核登记表，经审查、监测合格的在复核登记表上加盖“审核章”。逾期３个月未加盖“审核章”者，原“卫生许可证”自行失效。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（七）“卫生许可证”应用墨笔填写，字迹清楚。单位名称要写全称。“卫生许可证”应悬挂在明显处，以便监督检查。“卫生许可证”不得涂改、转让、倒卖、伪造。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（八）申请开业的公共场所经营单位经卫生防疫机构审查监测后确定不符合卫生要求者，应采取改善措施，达到卫生要求后发给“卫生许可证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　卫生行政部门应自卫生防疫机构接到“公共场所卫生许可证申请书”之次日起两个月内，对审查合格者签发“卫生许可证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（九）遗失“卫生许可证”者应及时到发证机关报失补领，歇业单位应到发证机关注销“卫生许可证”。　</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　第八条　公共场所经营单位和个人需防止危害健康事故的发生。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第九条　公共场所危害健康事故报告制度。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）报告范围：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　１．微小气候或空气质量不符合卫生标准所致的虚脱休克；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　２．生活饮水遭受污染或饮水污染所致的介水传染性疾病流行和中毒；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　３．公共用具、用水和卫生设施遭受污染所致传染性疾病、皮肤病；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　４．意外事故处致的一氧化碳、氨气、氯气、消毒杀虫剂等中毒。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）事故报告责任人是经营单位负责人及卫生负责人，其他人员也有义务报告。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）发生死亡或同时发生３名以上（含３名）受害病人时，事故报告责任人要在发生事故２４小时之内，电话报告当地卫生防疫机构，国内民航、铁路、交通、厂（场）矿等所属经营单位，应同时报告本系统卫生防疫机构，随即报告主管部门，必要时（如重大事故和可疑刑事案件等）必须同时报告公安部门。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）卫生防疫机构在接到报告２４小时内会同有关人员进行调查，并将调查结果及处理意见于１周内写成“公共场所危害健康事故现场调查报告书”，报送同级卫生行政部门、上级卫生防疫机构、事故单位的主管部门和事故单位，并建立档案。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十条　《条例》第九条中“妥善处理”包括抢救受害者脱离现场，迅速送病人到医疗机构，防止事故的继发。确保不扩大危害范围和不继续恶化环境，以及在不影响上述情况前提下保护好现场。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">第三章　卫生监督</span></strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十一条　各级卫生防疫机构的监督职责分工按卫生部发布的有关规定执行。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　上级卫生防疫机构有责任对下级卫生防疫机构公共场所卫生管理工作进行检查监督指导，各级卫生防疫机构之间要明确分工，避免遗漏或重复监测。省、自治区、直辖市卫生防疫机构对下级卫生防疫机构和当地民航、铁路、交通、厂（场）矿处理不当的违反《条例》的案件，有权纠正或重新处理。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十二条　各级卫生防疫机构必须定期向同级卫生行政部门及上一级卫生防疫机构上报公共场所卫生监督监测报表及有关资料。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十三条　公共场所卫生监督员职责：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）对管辖范围内公共场所进行卫生监督监测和卫生技术指导。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）宣传卫生知识，指导和协助有关部门对从业人员进行卫生知识培训。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）根据有关规定对违反《条例》有关条款的单位和个人提出处罚建议。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）参加对新建、扩建、改建的公共场所的选址和设计卫生审查和竣工验收。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（五）对公共场所进行现场检查，索取有关资料，包括取证照相、录音、录相等，调查处理公共场所发生危害健康事故。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（六）执行卫生防疫机构交付的其他任务。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十四条　根据工作需要卫生防疫机构可设置助理卫生监督员。助理卫生监督员在卫生监督员的指导下，协助卫生监督员执行上述工作。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十五条　公共场所卫生监督员、助理卫生监督员条件：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）政治思想好，遵纪守法，工作认真，作风正派，秉公办事，身体健康。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）卫生监督员具有医士以上（含医士）技术职称，从事公共卫生工作１年以上，掌握公共场所卫生监督监测业务和有关法规，有独立工作能力的专业人员。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）助理卫生监督员具有从事公共卫生工作１年以上，或具有医士（含医士）技术职称，熟悉公共场所卫生监督监测业务和有关法规，有一定的独立工作能力。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十六条　公共场所卫生监督员、助理卫生监督员守则：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）学习和掌握《条例》、《细则》及有关卫生标准和要求，不断提高政策水平和业务水平。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）执行任务做到依法办事，忠于职守，秉公办事，礼貌待人，不得滥用职权营私舞弊、索贿受贿。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）执行任务时应着装整齐，佩戴“中国卫生监督”证章，出示监督证件，严格执行有关规定，认真填写记录。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）严格执行请示报告制度。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十七条　公共场所卫生监督员、助理卫生监督员可按每３０至６０个公共场所设１人的比例配置。县以上（含县）卫生行政部门和卫生防疫机构从事公共场所卫生监督工作，符合卫生监督员和助理卫生监督员条件的可作为卫生监督员和助理卫生监督员。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十八条　公共场所卫生监督员由各级卫生行政部门提名，经省、自治区、直辖市卫生行政部门考核同意后，由各级卫生行政部门报同级人民政府批准发给证书。助理卫生监督员由县或地区级卫生防疫机构提名，经上一级卫生行政部门考核同意后，由县或地区级卫生行政部门批准发给证书。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第十九条　因工作调动或其他原因被免去公共场所卫生监督员和助理卫生监督员者，须及时交回证件和证章，并报省级卫生行政部门备案。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第二十条　民航、铁路、交通、厂（场）矿的公共场所卫生监督员的任免及数量，由国务院各主管部门参照本细则第十七条自定，报所在省、自治区、直辖市卫生行政部门备案。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第二十一条　公共场所建设项目设计卫生监督管理规定：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）凡《条例》第二条所列公共场所的新建、改建、扩建工程的选址、设计应符合有关卫生标准和要求，设计说明书中必须有卫生篇章。其内容包括设计依据、主要卫生问题、卫生保健设施、措施及其预期效果等。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（二）凡受周围环境质量影响和有职业危害以及对周围人群健康有影响的公共场所建设项目，必须执行建设项目卫生评价报告书制度。卫生评价报告书应在建设项目可行性研究阶段进行，施工设计前完成。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（三）建设项目的主管部门应将建设项目卫生评价报告书报卫生行政部门审批。审查同意的建设项目发给“建设项目卫生许可证”。建设单位取得“建设项目卫生许可证”后方可办理施工执照。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（四）设计及卫生评价报告书经卫生行政部门审查同意后，任何单位和个人不得擅自更改，需更改仍须取得卫生行政部门的同意。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（五）建设项目的竣工验收，应通知卫生防疫机构参加。验收合格者方可向卫生行政部门申请“卫生许可证”。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第二十二条　公共场所建设项目卫生评价资格单位由省级卫生行政部门审定并发给资格证书，报卫生部备案。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">第四章　罚　款</span></strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　第二十三条　对违反《条例》和本细则有关规定的单位或个人视情节轻重给予警告、罚款２０元至２万元、停业整顿、吊销“卫生许可证”的处罚。上述处罚可单独使用，也可合并使用。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　（一）有下列情形之一者给予警告处罚：</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　１．违反《条例》第六条，卫生制度不健全或从业人员未经卫生知识培训上岗者；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　２．违反本细则第五条第一款第一项，不按时进行健康检查者；</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; COLOR: rgb(61,61,61); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">　　３．符合《条例》第十四条第一款的规定，有一项主要卫生指标不合格者。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; WHITE-SPACE: normal; BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12pt/28px 宋体; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BORDER-TOP: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: inherit; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIG