ine-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">（一）拓宽线索来源。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">利用多种渠道和方式，为群众表达诉求、反映问题、提出意见建议、查询办理结果搭建平台。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">研究制定规范举报受理、线索核查的工作流程，明确举报线索与初核、立案、暂存、留存、了结的处置标准及程序，防止线索处置随意化。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">（二）严惩腐败行为。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">厅党组要加强对查案工作的领导，积极支持纪检监察机构查办案件，以零容忍态度惩治审计系统内部违纪违法行为，对发生在审计队伍中的腐败案件，要一查到底。重点查处违反“八项规定”、违反审计纪律、以审谋私、权钱交易、失职渎职等行为。对</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">审计人员违纪违法案件及时通报，总结教训，发挥反面教材的警示教育作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">（三）注重抓早抓小。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">本着对干部职工负责的态度，高度关注并全面掌握干部职工的思想、工作、纪律、作风状况，对审计队伍中存在的问题要早发现、早提醒、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">早报告、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">早纠正、早查处，并通过约谈、函询等方式，及时提醒审计人员对自身存在的苗头性问题加以纠正，防止小问题发展为大问题。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">七、大力支持纪检监察机构履行监督责任</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">（一）支持职能转变。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">认真落实纪律检查工作双重领导体制，切实加强对纪检监察工作的领导。纪检组长在党组中不分管其他业务工作，不兼任其他职务。进一步明晰纪检监察机构与机关党委（机关纪委）、人事处等其他内设机构在党风廉政建设中的职责分工，支持纪检监察机构把工作重心调整到监督、执纪、问责上来。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">（二）充实监督力量。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">按照形势和任务的要求健全纪检监察机构的机构设置，配齐配强纪检监察机构的领导班子和干部队伍。进一步加强兼职廉政监察员队伍建设，充分发挥他们在审计一线的提醒监督作用。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">（三）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">关心纪检监察干部。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">从政治上、工作上、生活上关心和爱护纪检监察干部，为他们创造良好的工作氛围和工作条件，激励他们坚守责任担当，在监督工作中敢于动真碰硬。加强对纪检监察干部的教育管理，督促他们以更高的标准、更严的纪律要求自己。加强对纪检监察干部的业务培训，不断提高履职能力。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; letter-spacing: -1px; background: transparent;\">中共湖北省审计厅党组<br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2014年7月3日</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-12-30 16:15:06', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 16:15:06', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 16:32:07', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
INSERT INTO `info_tcontent` VALUES ('402881e551f1d8670151f1f4cf660018', '湖北省审计厅落实党风廉政建设责任制实施办法', '', '湖北省', '湖北省', '', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">厅机关各处室局、各直属单位，各市、州、直管市、林区审计局：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>中共湖北省审计厅党组关于印发《湖北省审计厅落实党风廉政建设责任制实施办法》已经厅党组讨论通过，现印发给你们。厅机关各处室局和直属单位，要结合本单位实际认真抓好落实，各地审计机关可结合当地实际参照执行。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 35px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 41px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 41px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 41px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">中共湖北省审计厅党组</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 260px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2013年5月20日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 29px;font-family: 方正小标宋简体;background: transparent\">湖北省审计厅</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 29px;font-family: 方正小标宋简体;background: transparent\">落实党风廉政建设责任制实施办法</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 黑体;background: transparent\">第一章 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;总则</span>　　</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\">　　<span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第一条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">为加强党风廉政建设，明确领导班子、领导干部在党风廉政建设中应负的责任，从严治理审计队伍，努力打造审计铁军，保证和促进审计事业科学发展，根据中共中央、国务院《关于实行党风廉政建设责任制的规定》（中发〔2010〕19号），中共湖北省委、湖北省人民政府《关于实行党风廉政建设责任制的实施办法》（鄂发〔2011〕27号），审计署《落实党风廉政建设责任制实施办法》（审党发〔2011〕106号），结合审计厅实际，制定本实施办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\">　　<span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第二条&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">落实党风廉政建设责任制，要以邓小平理论、“三个代表”重要思想和科学发展观为指导，认真贯彻党的十八大和习近平总书记系列讲话精神，坚持党要管党、从严治党，坚持标本兼治、综合治理、惩防并举、注重预防，按照“力度统一论”要求，扎实推进惩治和预防腐败体系建设，保证党中央、国务院和省委、省政府以及审计署关于党风廉政建设的决策和部署的贯彻落实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\">　　<span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第三条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">落实党风廉政建设责任制，要坚持党组统一领导，党政齐抓共管，纪检监察组织协调，部门各负其责，依靠群众的支持和参与。要把党风廉政建设作为党的建设的重要内容，纳入领导班子、领导干部考核体系，与审计业务工作紧密结合，一起部署，一起落实，一起检查，一起考核。要坚持集体领导与个人分工负责相结合，谁主管，谁负责，一级抓一级，层层抓落实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第四条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">设立审计厅党风廉政建设领导小组，厅党组书记、厅长为组长，党组成员、其他厅领导为副组长；办公室、综合处、法规处、人事处、机关党委、驻厅监察室主要负责人为成员。领导小组下设办公室，由驻厅纪检组组长负责，日常工作由驻厅监察室承担。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 黑体;background: transparent\">第二章 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;责任定位</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第五条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">审计厅党组对党风廉政建设负主体责任，主要履行以下职责：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）贯彻落实党中央、国务院、中央纪委和省委、省政府、省纪委以及审计署关于党风廉政建设的部署和要求，结合实际制定党风廉政建设工作目标、工作计划和具体措施，召开专题会议部署工作，抓好责任分解，明确领导班子、领导干部的职责和任务分工，按照党组的工作部署推动工作落实；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">　　（二）开展党性党风党纪和廉洁教育，组织党员、干部学习党风廉政建设理论和法规制度，加强廉政文化建设；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">　　（三）贯彻落实党风廉政法规制度，结合实际，推进制度创新，建立健全风险防控机制，推进惩治和预防腐败体系建设，从源头上预防和治理腐败；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">　　（四）强化权力制约和监督，建立健全审计计划权、审计实施权和审计审理权既相互制约又相互协调的权力结构和运行机制，推进权力运行程序化和公开透明；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）监督检查厅机关各单位党风廉政建设情况和领导班子、领导干部廉洁从政情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（六）严格执行《党政领导干部选拨任用工作条例》及相关规定，防止和纠正选人用人上的不正之风；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">　　（七）加强审计系统的行风建设，充分发挥审计监督在纠正损害群众利益不正之风方面的作用；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（八）创新党风廉政建设工作机制，积极推进政务公开，促进依法审计、文明审计和从审廉洁；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（九）组织并支持纪检监察机构（人员）履行职责，及时听取工作汇报，解决其工作中遇到的困难和问题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第六条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">审计厅党组书记、厅长是职责范围内的党风廉政建设第一责任人，主要承担以下领导责任：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）贯彻落实中央、省委、省政府以及审计署有关党风廉政建设的部署和要求；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（二）结合审计工作实际，部署年度党风廉政建设工作任务，审定有关党风廉政建设的制度规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（三）抓好厅班子成员及各单位主要负责人党风廉政建设规定的执行；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（四）督促厅班子成员及各单位主要负责人廉洁自律；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）对党风廉政建设重要工作亲自部署、重大问题亲自过问、重点环节亲自协调、重要案件亲自督办；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（六）支持驻厅纪检组长协助厅党组开展党风廉政建设以及案件查办工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（七）率先垂范，模范遵守有关党风廉政建设的各项规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（八）完成省委、省政府交办的其他相关工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第七条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">分管厅领导对职责范围内的党风廉政建设负主要领导责任，主要承担以下领导责任：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）协助厅党组书记、厅长抓好审计厅的党风廉政建设工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（二）贯彻落实中央、省委、省政府、审计署以及厅党组有关党风廉政建设的部署和要求；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（三）提出制定和完善有关党风廉政建设制度规定的意见和建议；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（四）对党风廉政建设方面出现的问题及时提出意见和建议；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）按照分工抓好职责范围内和分管处室的党风廉政建设工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（六）模范遵守有关党风廉政建设的各项规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（七）完成厅党组交办的其他相关工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第八条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">驻厅纪检组长对职责范围内的党风廉政建设负监督责任，主要承担以下领导责任：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）贯彻落实中央、省委、省政府和省纪委有关党风廉政建设的部署和要求；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（二）协助厅党组抓好党风廉政建设工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（三）监督检查厅党组及其成员贯彻落实党风廉政建设情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（四）向省纪委报告党风廉政建设的有关情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）向厅党组提出有关党风廉政建设的意见和建议。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第九条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">厅机关各处室局、各直属单位主要负责人，对本单位党风廉政建设负直接责任：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）贯彻落实中央、省委、省政府、审计署以及厅党组关于党风廉政建设的部署和要求，分析本单位的党风廉政建设状况，研究制定工作计划、目标要求和具体措施，并组织实施；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（二）组织学习党风廉政建设的法律法规、制度规定以及重要文件，抓好本单位的党性党风党纪教育；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（三）贯彻厅党组和厅党风廉政建设领导小组下发的党风廉政建设的制度规定，结合本单位实际，制定和完善具体实施办法或措施，并督促落实；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（四）履行监督职责，对干部廉洁从政和审计组执行审计纪律情况进行监督检查，并向分管厅领导和厅党风廉政建设领导小组报告有关情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）按照</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">“实、高、新、严、细”的要求，从严管理干部队伍，切实解决“四风”方面存在的突出问题；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（六）及时向分管厅领导和厅党风廉政建设领导小组报告本单位出现的违纪违法问题，积极主动配合纪检监察部门调查处理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（七）带头遵守有关党风廉政建设各项规定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">按照部门各负其责的要求，厅机关相关单位根据各自的职责，分别对厅党风廉政建设工作承担以下责任：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）办公室牵头负责：贯彻落实“八项规定”、“六条意见”及“三公经费”等规定，抓好政务制度、政务公开、各类专项整治、财务管理、群众来信来访、机关内部管理制度制定及执行等工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（二）法规处牵头负责：厅机关法律法规宣传教育、制定或修订与审计权力运行相关规范和制度、对审计执法相关制度执行情况进行监督检查和责任追究、配合有关部门做好对责任追究案件的调查处理工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（三）人事处牵头负责：落实上级和厅党组制定的各项干部人事法规制度，查办党组成员述职述廉及重大事项报告等工作，严格执行公务人员出国（境）管理的有关规定，督促检查厅机关办公纪律执行情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（四）机关党委（纪委）牵头负责：厅机关党务公开工作，厅机关党风廉政宣传教育、廉政文化建设和机关作风纪律建设，科级（含）以下党员干部违法违纪问题查处工作，组织协调厅机关反腐倡廉工作任务；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）驻厅监察室牵头负责：按照上级有关党风廉政建设的部署和要求，对厅内党风廉政建设工作提出意见建议，监督检查全省审计系统党风廉政建设责任制落实情况，牵头对各单位落实党风廉政建设各项法规制度、审计纪律的监督检查，调查核实处级党员、干部违法违纪问题及其他重要案件，受理厅机关及直属单位礼品、礼金等登记与上交管理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（六）机关后勤服务中心牵头负责：厅机关和直属单位基本建设、固定资产实物管理、重大采购和招投标等相关制度的建立及执行，干部职工住房、厅机关办公用房，公务接待，公务用车配备、使用等制度规定的贯彻执行；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（七）各业务处（局）负责：落实厅党风廉政建设领导小组提出的年度反腐倡廉责任分解及任务分工。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 黑体;background: transparent\">第三章 &nbsp;检查考核与监督</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十一条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">厅党风廉政建设领导小组负责对厅机关各单位和主要负责人党风廉政建设责任制落实情况进行检查考核。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十二条&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">检查考核工作每年进行一次。厅党风廉政建设领导小组办公室提出检查考核工作方案，报党风廉政建设领导小组批准后实施。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十三条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">检查考核工作与年度岗位目标考核同步进行，采取自查和检查相结合的方式，考核覆盖面为100%。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十四条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">考核内容主要为分解责任和年度反腐倡廉工作安排。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十五条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">在厅年度审计工作和党建工作安排时，要将党风廉政建设作为重要内容任务，统一部署；考核检查党的建设、领导班子和领导干部、审计业务工作时，要把党风廉政建设责任制落实情况作为重要内容，统一考核。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十六条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">检查考核情况及时向厅党组报告并在适当范围内通报。对检查考核中发现的问题，要及时研究解决，督促整改落实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十七条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">建立和完善检查考核结果运用制度。检查考核结果作为单位总体评价和党员干部成绩评定、奖励惩处、选拔任用的依据之一。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十八条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">厅领导和各处室局、直属单位主要负责人，落实党风廉政建设责任制的情况应当列为民主生活会和述职述廉内容，并接受群众评议。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 黑体;background: transparent\">第四章 &nbsp;责任追究</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第十九条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">有下列情形之一的，实行责任追究：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（一）对党风廉政建设工作领导不力，执行有关规定不严，以致职责范围内发生违反审计纪律、廉政规定、财经制度等问题，造成不良影响的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（二）对上级领导机关交办的党风廉政建设责任范围内的事项不传达贯彻、不安排部署、不督促落实，或者拒不办理的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（三）对本单位发现的严重违法违纪行为隐瞒不报、压案不查的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（四）疏于监督管理，致使领导班子成员或者直接管辖的下属发生严重违法违纪问题的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（五）违反规定选拔任用干部，或者用人失察、失误造成恶劣影响的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（六）放任、包庇、纵容下属人员违反审计、财经等法律法规，弄虚作假或者滥用审计权力以权谋私的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">（七）有其他违反党风廉政建设责任制行为的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第二十条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">对违反党风廉政建设责任制的当事人，视情节轻重，依据纪律条例和相关制度规定予以相应处理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 黑体;background: transparent\">第五章 &nbsp;附 &nbsp;则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;text-align: center;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第二十一条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">本实施办法由厅党风廉政建设领导小组负责解释。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">第二十二条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;background: transparent\">本实施办法自印发之日起施行。1999年印发的《湖北省审计厅落实党风廉政建设责任制的实施办法》（鄂审发〔1999〕25号）同时废止。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-12-30 16:15:31', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 16:15:31', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 16:31:59', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
