; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">二○一二年二月十五日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; background: transparent;\">湖北省审计机关</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; background: transparent;\">审计组岗位廉政风险防控办法（试行）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第一章 &nbsp;总 &nbsp;则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第一条 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">为加强审计组廉政建设，防控审计一线岗位廉政风险，根据中共湖北省纪委、湖北省监察厅、湖北省审计厅、湖北省预防腐败局《关于加强审计执法廉政风险防控工作的意见》等规定，结合我省审计工作实际，制定本办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法所称审计组，是指审计机关履行法定监督职责、实施具体审计项目的工作小组，其岗位包括：审计组组长、主审、审计人员。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">岗位廉政风险，是指审计组行使审计职权过程中可能导致不廉洁行为发生的条件和因素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计组岗位廉政风险防控，是指审计机关对审计组和审计人员行使审计职权过程中所涉及岗位存在的廉政风险，有针对性地进行风险排查、风险教育、完善制度、实时监控、预警纠偏，有效防范和控制不廉洁行为发生的综合管理和控制活动。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">湖北省各级审计机关派出的各类审计项目审计组实行廉政风险防控适用本办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计组岗位廉政风险防控，坚持以人为本的理念，坚持廉政风险防控与审计业务工作相结合、内部防控与外部监督相结合、规范执法行为与完善制度机制相结合、提升审计质量与提高审计效能相结合、授权履职与考核问责相结合的原则。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第五条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计组岗位廉政风险防控，以规范审计人员执法行为为核心，以查找廉政风险为基础，以完善防控措施为重点，以强化管理责任为抓手，以加强制度建设和监督检查为保障，着力构建审计组岗位廉政风险防控长效机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第六条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计组岗位廉政风险防控工作在各级审计机关统一领导下，由纪检监察机构（组织）牵头，机关党组织和法制、审理、计划管理、人事管理、行政管理、财务管理、信息化建设等部门（机构）共同组织，审计组所在审计业务部门（以下简称业务部门）负责实施，审计组具体落实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二章 &nbsp;防控重点</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第七条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在审计准备环节</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）不按规定执行审计人员回避，违反规定由外部人员担任审计组组长或主审，内部重要管理事项及职责分工等不明确、不具体；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）违反规定聘用外部人员，或擅自将审计业务交给外部审计力量实施；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）不按规定安排审计项目进度，审计实施时间与项目工作量明显不合理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）审计经费预算未列入审计项目计划，预算编制明显不合理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第八条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在审计实施环节</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）违反规定由审计人员1人单独调查取证、与被审计单位及有关人员接触，或商谈审计事项处理意见；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）故意或借故不查询或不深入查询有关单位账户、个人存款账户，擅自或授意他人变更审计证据内容；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）违反规定由外部人员单独调查取证、与被审计单位商谈审计事项、交换处理意见，或以审计机关名义、审计职权和审计成果谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）不作判断或评估，擅自或借故利用外部人员的专业咨询、专业鉴定或直接将中介机构工作结果作为审计证据；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）故意泄漏知悉的国家秘密、商业秘密和个人隐私，擅自将取得和形成的审计资料和结论对外披露；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）故意或借故拖延采取、不采取或不报告应当采取相应的证据保全措施或其他必要的应对措施，或放任有关人员妨碍审计调查、串供、毁证、逃逸等行为；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）不按规定受理信访举报事项，故意或借故对交办的信访举报中的重要问题或案件线索不调查核实或拖延调查核实，或擅自扣压、销毁或篡改证据，包庇当事人或向当事人泄漏信访内容；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）违反审计纪律“八不准”规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（九）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第九条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在审计报告环节</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）借故不按规定程序讨论确定审计报告事项，重大问题未形成统一意见或结论；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）提交的审计报告内容虚假，避重就轻，审计评价不真实、不公正，审计结果定性不准确，故意为相关单位或人员开脱责任；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）瞒报审计发现的问题或重要案件线索；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）隐瞒、变更查出的违法违纪事实；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）篡改、隐匿、丢弃、销毁审计证据，歪曲、捏造证据材料；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）擅自以个人、审计机关或审计机关负责人名义向被审计单位发表审计意见、作出审计结论；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）滥用自由裁量权，借故从轻、减轻、免除处理处罚，故意不按规定追缴或责令清退违纪违规款物，或擅自减少追缴数量，或故意追缴、清退不及时、不到位；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）借故不提出移送需要纪检监察或司法机关追究有关人员党纪政纪或刑事责任、有关主管机关或单位纠正、处理处罚的事项，或与相关单位及人员私下交易以处理处罚代替移送问责；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（九）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在审计质量控制环节</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未发现或纠正审计实施方案编制中的重要问题；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）未发现或未纠正审计证据不适当、不充分，审计工作底稿不真实、不完整，审计结论不正确、不恰当的问题；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）未发现或未纠正审计组起草的审计文书、审计信息反映的问题、或提出的审计处理处罚意见严重失实；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）擅自或故意删除，或授意或强令审计人员删除审计记录等资料相关内容；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）隐瞒不报或不如实报告审计人员发现的重要问题；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十一条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在内部监管环节</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为:</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）进点前不按要求组织廉政教育，未明确兼职廉政监察员；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）进点时不按规定在被审计单位宣布并张贴审计纪律公示、告知监督举报方式等信息；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）审计期间教育不实、管理不严、监督不力，审计组组长、兼职廉政监察员未尽监管责任，对苗头性问题未及时采取教育、提醒、制止等措施；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）未将外部人员纳入审计组统一管理，教育缺位、监管失控；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）未履行规定程序，擅自或借故调整、使用审计人员；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）故意拖延现场审计时间，审计成本控制不严；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）违反外勤经费管理规定，套取报领经费补助；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）违反规定安排住宿、就餐，未实行就餐、住宿登记管理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（九）审计结束时未对执行审计纪律和经费自理情况进行自查、小结并在被审计单位公示；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（十）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三章 &nbsp;防控措施</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十二条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">全面排查审计组岗位廉政风险，重点排查落实廉政教育、执行审计业务、强化质量控制、加强内部监管、审计经费开支等方面的风险，确定风险等级，建立审计组岗位廉政风险库，并</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">根据风险新形式、新特点，及时调整充实审计组岗位廉政风险库。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十三条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">修订完善审计组廉政责任制，明确审计组组长、主审、审计人员岗位职责及问责办法，细化工作内容、方法、标准和要求。健全统一组织审计项目审计组廉政责任体系，实行审计机关负责人、业务部门负责人、派出审计组的审计机关主要负责人、审计组组长四级廉政建设责任体系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十四条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善兼职廉政监察员选配、报备、培训、激励、保护等制度，建立兼职廉政监察员汇报工作、报告情况、提出建议等工作机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十五条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">落实<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK3\"></a>审计人员廉政档案制度，实行审计组廉政建设情况纳入业务部门党风廉政建设责任制，与干部考核使用、审计项目质量检查评比、目标责任制考核、综合量化考核挂钩。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十六条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">加强审计组岗位廉政教育，以审计组岗位职责、岗位廉政纪律、岗位职业道德、岗位廉政风险及危害等为重点内容，整理岗位模范标兵、岗位先进典型、岗位廉政文化、岗位警示案例等教育素材，创新审计组岗位廉政教育方式方法，建立视频会议、远程网络、手机短信等教育平台和载体，丰富审计机关教育资源、网络教育资源、审计现场教育资源，把审计机关廉政教育“规定动作”与审计组岗位廉政教育“自选动作”有机结合。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十七条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善执行审计纪律和廉政规定配套制度，落实进点前审计纪律教育制度，进点时审计纪律与审计通知书同时送达、审计执法公示、审计承诺制度，审计期间经常提醒教育、不定期向审计机关负责人、业务部门负责人、机关党组织、纪检监察机构（组织）汇报制度，审计结束后执行审计纪律和外勤经费自理情况自查、小结，推行将自查情况在被审计单位和审计机关公示制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十八条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">加强审计组党组织建设，建立审计组临时党支部（党小组）制度，明确审计组临时党支部（党小组）思想政治教育、廉政建设、文化活动等职责，提高审计组解决问题、处理问题能力，充分发挥党组织战斗堡垒作用和党员先锋模范作用。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十九条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">实行审计组有关信息报送制度，进点前将审计实施方案、审计组人员及分工（包括借聘人员及单位、统一组织审计项目所有审计组及人员）、兼职廉政监察员、临时党支部（党小组）、审计地点、住宿宾馆等信息报纪检监察机构（组织）、机关党组织及法制、审理、计划、财务等部门备查。实行审计组执行审计纪律、外勤经费自理情况报监察机构备案、财务部门审核报领制度，统一组织审计项目审计组报业务部门汇总审核后分别报监察机构备案、财务部门审核报领制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善审计现场管理办法、项目进度控制办法，推行送达审计、审计组组长现场跟班工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十一条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK7\"></a>审计组成员选配机制，推行审计组组长、主审公开竞争、双向选择和审计人员交叉轮岗等办法，严格执行主动回避等措施。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十二条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">推行审计人员工作分离制，采取政府投资项目跟踪审计人员与决算审计人员分离工作模式，外部人员不参与调查取证、不与被审计单位单独接触等规定。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十三条&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK2\"></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善统一组织审计项目审计工作管理规定</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">，建立上级审计机关、派出审计组的审计机关、审计组工作所在地审计机关之间统筹指挥、组织协调、沟通配合、责任分担机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十四条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">认真执行《湖北省<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK1\"></a>政府投资项目审计操作规程》，细化建设、勘察、设计、施工、监理、采购、供货等单位和环节的审计或审计调查程序及各级责任主体，建立健全政府投资项目审计组织、审计实施、审核复核、质量检查、廉政建设及责任追究等制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十五条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格执行外部审计力量参与审计工作纳入审计项目计划管理、审计经费预算管理、聘用合同管理、廉政承诺等规定，严格控制、严格审批外部审计力量参与审计工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十六条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">加强外部人员审前业务培训和廉政教育、认同教育，增强国家审计意识，将外部人员纳入审计组统一管理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十七条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格执行外部人员不得担任审计组组长和主审、不得单独执行审计业务规定，严禁委托审计。实行审计组对外部审计力量提出考核、使用、付费等意见和建议规定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十八条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格执行<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK8\"></a>审计处罚自由裁量权指导规则和标准，细化对单位、个人审计处罚的法律依据、种类、幅度和审批程序、权限。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十九条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">探索建立审计执法典型案例库，推行审计执法参照先例制度，制定滥用自由裁量权责任追究办法。完善告知、听证、回避等程序规则。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">推行审计外勤经费自理，落实审计经费纳入政府财政预算保障规定，在法律法规和政策规定范围内多渠道解决审计经费不足，切断审计机关与被审计单位和中介机构之间经济联系。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十一条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK10\"></a>审计外勤经费计划管理办法，实行审计外勤经费预算与审计项目计划统一制定、统一申报、统一审核、统一管理规定。推行根据上年度审计外勤经费支出额、审计项目工作量测算确定本年度审计外勤经费总额，根据本年度审计项目测算确定各审计项目的外勤经费数额。完善审计项目变化追加审计外勤经费审批程序。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十二条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">细化<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK11\"></a>审计外勤经费管理办法，明确住宿、就餐、交通、通讯及杂费标准，制定开支项目、适用范围、使用管理和审核报销规定，采取定点食宿、合同议价、包干使用、实报实销等形式，实行机关财务室统一结算、转账或公务卡等结账方式。实行审计组就餐、住宿和使用被审计单位交通工具等办公设备登记制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十三条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">加强审计质量控制，严格执行《国家审计准则》和《<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK12\"></a>湖北省审计机关审计项目审理操作规程》，严格执行审计组审核、业务部门复核、法规（审理）部门审理制度。认真落实审计业务会议集体研究审计报告、审计决定、移送处理等制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十四条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">实行审计组通过审计现场实施系统（AO）和审计管理系统（OA）交互上传电子资料，法制（审理）机构实施网上审理。法制（审理）、计划、监察、财务等部门和机构，对审计质量、审计进度、审计纪律、审计成本等情况实施跟踪督查。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十五条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">推行审计组工作绩效考核评估办法，对审计进度、审计质量、审计成果、审计费用、审计纪律等进行综合量化评估，提出审计组绩效报告。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十六条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">推行</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\" name=\"OLE_LINK16\"></a>审计成本核算控制机制，建立审计预算、成本决算制度，制定审计成本核算模型和标准，加强审计绩效管理。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四章 &nbsp;预警处置</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十七条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立审计权力运行风险电子监控系统，将审计组岗位廉政风险防控纳入信息化管理，利用OA和AO系统等平台，采取“制度+科技”的方式，对审计组行使职权过程中可能发生的执法风险、廉政风险、效能风险实行全方位监控。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十八条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立审计组岗位廉政风险收集机制，多渠道、多方位全面收集风险信息。在审计机关和党代表、人大代表、政协委员、特邀监察员、特邀审计员、政风行风监督员、新闻单位代表、被审计单位中聘请内部、外部风险信息员。通过政风行风评议、政风行风热线、经济责任审计、内部审计等相关工作收集风险信息。通过信访举报、问卷调查、网上调查、廉政巡查、廉政回访、专项检查、执法和效能监察、述职述廉、民主生活会等相关活动收集风险信息。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十九条&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">纪检监察机构（组织）对收集的风险信息及时进行汇总、评估、分析，根据风险等级、风险类别及预控措施，通过书面函、电子监控系统、手机短信等形式向相关单位和人员发出询问、告知、提示等预警通知，采取批评教育、信访约谈、诫勉谈话等方式进行风险预警。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四十条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">受到预警的单位和人员，应当及时采取措施整改、说明情况、剖析原因，制定和完善防范措施，并反馈处置结果。纪检监察机构应当加强对预警处置措施落实情况的督查，对整改不及时、落实不到位的，应根据有关规定实行问责或组织处理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第五章 &nbsp;附 &nbsp;则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四十一条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各级审计机关应当将审计组岗位廉政风险防控工作纳入党风廉政建设责任制检查和目标考核内容，建立审计组岗位廉政风险防控工作考核制度，加强工作指导、督促、检查和考核，对不认真落实防控措施的单位和个人按有关规定实施责任追究。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四十二条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各级</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计机关应当结合本办法制定具体实施细则和相关配套制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四十三条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法由驻湖北省审计厅纪检组负责解释。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四十四条 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法自发布之日起施行。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-12-30 16:15:55', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 16:15:55', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 16:31:52', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
