center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; background: transparent;\">湖北省审计机关利用外部审计力量</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; background: transparent;\">廉政风险防控办法（试行）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第一章 &nbsp;总 &nbsp;则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第一条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">为规范审计机关利用外部审计力量参与审计工作行为，有效防范利用外部审计力量过程中的廉政风险，根据湖北省纪委、湖北省监察厅、湖北省审计厅、湖北省预防腐败局《关于加强审计执法廉政风险防控工作的意见》和审计署《聘请外部人员参与审计工作管理办法》等规定，结合我省审计工作实际，制定本办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法所称利用外部审计力量，指审计机关遇有审计力量不足、相关专业知识不能满足审计工作需要时，根据法律规定从外部聘请相关专业人员参与或利用相关机构等形成的工作结果实施审计（含专项审计调查，下同）工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">外部审计力量，主要包括：社会中介机构和其他专业机构及其专业人员、专家，以及所形成的工作结果、提供的咨询意见或专业鉴定意见等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">廉政风险，是指审计机关在利用外部审计力量行使审计职权过程中可能导致不廉洁行为发生的条件和因素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控，是指审计机关对在利用外部审计力量行使审计职权所涉及的招标聘用、项目分配以及管理、使用、考评、付费等环节和过程中存在的廉政风险，进行风险排查、实时监控、预警纠偏、完善制度，以预防腐败行为发生的综合管理和控制活动。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">湖北省各级审计机关利用外部审计力量参与规定范围内的审计项目实行廉政风险防控适用本办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量参与的审计项目范围主要有：固定资产投资审计，企业和金融机构资产、负债、损益及其主要负责人任期经济责任审计，事业单位、社会团体和其他社会组织财务收支及其主要负责人任期经济责任审计，资源环境项目审计，社会保障项目审计，国外贷援款项目审计，以及其他需要利用外部审计力量参与的审计。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控，应着眼于治本、预防和制度建设，坚持内部防控与外部监督相结合、事前防范与预警处置相结合、质量管理与流程监管相结合、强化规范与健全完善相结合、授权履职与考评问责相结合的原则。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第五条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控，以规范外部审计力量利用全过程为核心，以查找廉政风险为基础，以完善防范措施为重点，以强化管理责任为抓手，以加强制度建设和监督检查为保障，着力构建利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控长效机制。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: red; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第六条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控工作在各级审计机关的统一领导下，由纪检监察机构（组织）牵头，法制、审理、计划管理、人事管理、行政管理、财务管理、信息化建设等部门（机构）共同组织，利用外部审计力量的相关部门（机构）及外部审计力量负责实施和具体落实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">防控重点</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第七条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在招投标环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未按规定实施招投标规程，未坚持公平、公开、公正原则，故意或借故规避有关部门（机构）监督；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）在制定招标方案和招标书时，故意或授意有选择性地针对某个对象设定条件和标准；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）在组建评标委员会、随机抽选评标专家时，故意选取或不选取某个对象；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）开标评标时，故意或授意受理不符合规定条件和标准的对象，或人为影响评标专家独立评判；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）在评估投标文件、汇总评标结果中弄虚作假、徇私舞弊，为本人、亲属及特定关系人谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）未建立外部审计力量备选库和评委专家库充实调整和淘汰更新机制，故意或授意将考核不合格、淘汰退出的对象继续聘请入库；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第八条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在审计项目分配环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）违规插手、干预审计项目分配，为本人、亲属及特定关系人谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）故意或借故规避项目随机分配程序和有关机构监督，人为选择参与审计项目对象，从中收受好处，以及为外部审计力量争取项目拉拢腐蚀其他人员；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）业务部门违规申报需求计划，未按规定对拟聘用外部审计力量的数量、人数、专业要求和费用预算等情况进行测算、汇总，擅自夸大需求计划；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）计划管理部门未按规定程序及时对聘用申请计划进行审核、报批，聘用申请计划未经厅（局）长办公会议研究审定即纳入年度审计项目计划，财务管理部门未按规定审核聘请费用即纳入年度审计经费预算，法制、审理部门未制定和报批年度聘用计划，或报批后未及时通知备选成员单位参加现场选取；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）未采取随机产生方式选取参与审计项目的对象，或人为操作故意选取或不选取某个对象；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）未按规定当场宣布和登记选取结果、组织相关人员在选取结果备案书上签字、签订聘用协议和公布选取结果；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第九条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在参与审计工作环节，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未严格把关，参与审计项目的单位选派的外部人员不能胜任工作，或中途擅自更换人员、无故脱岗离岗，未能有效履行协议；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">违规由外部人员担任审计组组长或主审；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">放任或授意由外部人员独立调查取证、私自与被审计单位商谈审计事项、交换处理意见，或以审计机关名义、审计职权和审计成果，为本人、亲属及特定关系人谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">未及时对外部人员进行督导和业务复核，不作判断或评估，擅自或借故利用外部人员的专业咨询、专业鉴定或直接将其工作结果作为审计证据；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: transparent;\">（五）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计结束后，组长或主审在填报外部审计力量工作情况考评表时，弄虚作假、迁就照顾；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在内部监管环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未将外部人员纳入审计组统一教育、严格管理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">未组织外部人员进行国家审计法律、法规、规章及审计业务培训和审计纪律、职业道德教育，或组织业务培训、廉政教育流于形式；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）接受外部人员的馈赠或回扣，参加由其安排的娱乐活动，向聘请的外部人员提不合理要求，为本人、亲属及特定关系人办理与审计无关事项；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）放任外部人员在聘用期内从事社会兼职工作，或以审计机关名义从事与审计事项无关的活动，或以不正当手段拉拢审计机关人员，故意隐瞒审计发现问题或与被审计单位串通舞弊，从被审计单位获取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）故意泄漏知悉的国家秘密、审计秘密、商业秘密和个人隐私，将取得和形成的审计资料和结论擅自对外披露或者用于与审计无关的目的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）违规报销因公因私费用，虚报冒领外部审计力量的外勤补助；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）违反审计职业道德规范和审计纪律“八不准”规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十一条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在经费保障环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未编报或违规编报聘用经费预算；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）未将聘用经费纳入年度经费预算；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）故意或授意挤占、挪用、侵占、套取、调配聘用经费；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）将审减额与审计经费直接挂钩，或以业务介绍费、劳务报酬等方式向外部审计力量收取一定比例的费用；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）从外部审计力量的审减收费中留存部分经费，以聘请外部审计力量名义向被审计单位收费，授意或放任其与被审计单位商议所需审计费用，或要求被审计单位直接将审计费用支付给外部审计力量；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）未经考评或考评后未按规定标准支付聘用经费，故意或授意拖延支付聘用经费，从中收受好处；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）未执行聘用经费由审计机关支付规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">防控措施</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十二条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">全面排查利用外部审计力量廉政风险，重点排查招标聘用、项目分配、参与审计、内部监管、经费保障、监督制约等方面的风险点，建立利用外部审计力量廉政风险库。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十三条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">修订完善利用外部审计力量廉政责任制，明确监察、法制、审理、计划管理、人事管理、行政管理、财务管理、信息化建设、业务部门等部门（机构）在利用外部审计力量过程中的职责及问责办法，细化工作内容、方法、标准和要求。实行外部审计力量廉政建设情况与职业道德诚信档案、审计项目质量检查评比、目标责任制考核、综合量化考核、聘用费用和工资待遇管理等挂钩机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十四条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善利用外部审计力量参与规定范围审计项目的制度规定，以及配套的招标投标管理、资质资格审查、经费管理、综合考核等相关制度机制，明确外部审计力量参与审计工作的条件和范围，细化所需外部审计力量的资质、资格等条件，合理制定经费标准，严格控制、严格审批外部审计力量参与审计工作。积极探索和建立审计业务专家咨询委员会，科学调配和整合审计资源，有效借助外部审计力量对审计项目的技术支持、专业意见和专业鉴定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十五条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格实行利用外部审计力量需求测算、申请审批以及纳入年度项目计划和经费预算管理等制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十六条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格执行外部审计力量招投标制度，建立评标专家库和外部审计力量备选库。完善评标专家库随机产生、充实调整等机制。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: red; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十七条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">实行审计项目随机分配制度，采取随机摇号等方式从备选库中选取参与审计项目的外部力量。严格执行合同协议、廉政承诺等管理办</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十八条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">加强外部审计力量的审前业务培训和廉政教育、认同教育，增强国家审计意识和职业道德素养。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十九条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">认真落实外部人员纳入审计组统一管理的全员责任制，严格执行外部人员不得担任审计组组长和主审、不得单独执行审计业务、严禁委托审计或独立审计等制度规定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">探索建立审计机关与财政、建设、工商、税务等部门和单位的协调沟通机制，实行建立诚信档案、准入退出、社会公示和“黑名单”等制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十一条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立完善利用外部审计力量的审计业务质量、审计职业道德、审计纪律、审计绩效等考核和奖惩办法，认真落实审计组提出考核、使用、付费等意见、建议的规定，业务部门与法制、审理、监察、计划管理、人事管理、财务管理等部门（机构）综合考核机制。探索实行廉政保证金、质量保证金等机制，完善对外部审计力量的责任追究和动态淘汰等机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十二条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">探索建立聘用经费保障机制，推行聘用经费纳入年度政府财政预算、申请项目专项经费、列入项目总预算报批、财政转移支付等方式，多种渠道、规范合理解决所需经费。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">预警处置</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十三条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立审计权力运行风险电子监控系统，将利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控纳入信息化管理，利用</span>OA<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">和</span>AO<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">等平台，采取“制度</span>+<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">科技”的方式，对利用外部审计力量全过程中可能发生的廉政风险，实行流程管理和电子监控。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十四条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">将利用外部审计力量廉政风险信息纳入审计机关廉政风险信息收集机制，充分发挥信息员作用，利用相关工作和活动，多渠道、多方位全面收集风险信息。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十五条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">纪检监察机构（组织）要对收集的风险信息及时进行汇总、分析和评估，根据风险等级、风险类别及预控措施，通过书面函、电子监控系统、手机短信等形式向相关单位和个人发出询问、告知、提示等预警通知，采取谈心疏导、批评教育、信访约谈、诫勉谈话等方式进行风险预警。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十六条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">受到预警的单位和个人，应当及时说明情况、剖析原因，制定和完善整改措施，并反馈处置结果。纪检监察机构（组织）应当加强对预警处置措施落实情况的监督，对整改不及时、落实不到位的，应根据有关规定实行问责或组织处理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第五章</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">附</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十七条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各级审计机关应将利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控工作纳入党风廉政建设责任制检查和目标考核内容，建立利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控工作考核制度，加强工作指导、督促、检查和考核，对不认真落实防控措施的单位和个人按有关规定实施责任追究。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十八条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各级审计机关应结合本办法制定具体实施细则和相关配套制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十九条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法由驻湖北省审计厅纪检组负责解释。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法自发布之日起施行。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-12-30 16:16:21', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 16:16:21', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 16:31:44', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
INSERT INTO `info_tcontent` VALUES ('402881e551f1d8670151f1f5eb8a001b', '湖北省审计机关利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控办法（试行）', '', '湖北省', '湖北省', '', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各市、州、直管市、神农架林区审计局，厅机关各处、室、局，各直属事业单位</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">《湖北省审计机关利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控办法（试行）》，已经厅领导审定通过，现印发你们，请认真遵照执行。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">二○一二年三月六日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; background: transparent;\">湖北省审计机关利用外部审计力量</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; background: transparent;\">廉政风险防控办法（试行）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第一章 &nbsp;总 &nbsp;则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第一条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">为规范审计机关利用外部审计力量参与审计工作行为，有效防范利用外部审计力量过程中的廉政风险，根据湖北省纪委、湖北省监察厅、湖北省审计厅、湖北省预防腐败局《关于加强审计执法廉政风险防控工作的意见》和审计署《聘请外部人员参与审计工作管理办法》等规定，结合我省审计工作实际，制定本办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法所称利用外部审计力量，指审计机关遇有审计力量不足、相关专业知识不能满足审计工作需要时，根据法律规定从外部聘请相关专业人员参与或利用相关机构等形成的工作结果实施审计（含专项审计调查，下同）工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">外部审计力量，主要包括：社会中介机构和其他专业机构及其专业人员、专家，以及所形成的工作结果、提供的咨询意见或专业鉴定意见等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">廉政风险，是指审计机关在利用外部审计力量行使审计职权过程中可能导致不廉洁行为发生的条件和因素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控，是指审计机关对在利用外部审计力量行使审计职权所涉及的招标聘用、项目分配以及管理、使用、考评、付费等环节和过程中存在的廉政风险，进行风险排查、实时监控、预警纠偏、完善制度，以预防腐败行为发生的综合管理和控制活动。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">湖北省各级审计机关利用外部审计力量参与规定范围内的审计项目实行廉政风险防控适用本办法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量参与的审计项目范围主要有：固定资产投资审计，企业和金融机构资产、负债、损益及其主要负责人任期经济责任审计，事业单位、社会团体和其他社会组织财务收支及其主要负责人任期经济责任审计，资源环境项目审计，社会保障项目审计，国外贷援款项目审计，以及其他需要利用外部审计力量参与的审计。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控，应着眼于治本、预防和制度建设，坚持内部防控与外部监督相结合、事前防范与预警处置相结合、质量管理与流程监管相结合、强化规范与健全完善相结合、授权履职与考评问责相结合的原则。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第五条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控，以规范外部审计力量利用全过程为核心，以查找廉政风险为基础，以完善防范措施为重点，以强化管理责任为抓手，以加强制度建设和监督检查为保障，着力构建利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控长效机制。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: red; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第六条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控工作在各级审计机关的统一领导下，由纪检监察机构（组织）牵头，法制、审理、计划管理、人事管理、行政管理、财务管理、信息化建设等部门（机构）共同组织，利用外部审计力量的相关部门（机构）及外部审计力量负责实施和具体落实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">防控重点</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第七条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在招投标环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未按规定实施招投标规程，未坚持公平、公开、公正原则，故意或借故规避有关部门（机构）监督；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）在制定招标方案和招标书时，故意或授意有选择性地针对某个对象设定条件和标准；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）在组建评标委员会、随机抽选评标专家时，故意选取或不选取某个对象；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）开标评标时，故意或授意受理不符合规定条件和标准的对象，或人为影响评标专家独立评判；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）在评估投标文件、汇总评标结果中弄虚作假、徇私舞弊，为本人、亲属及特定关系人谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）未建立外部审计力量备选库和评委专家库充实调整和淘汰更新机制，故意或授意将考核不合格、淘汰退出的对象继续聘请入库；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第八条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在审计项目分配环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）违规插手、干预审计项目分配，为本人、亲属及特定关系人谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）故意或借故规避项目随机分配程序和有关机构监督，人为选择参与审计项目对象，从中收受好处，以及为外部审计力量争取项目拉拢腐蚀其他人员；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）业务部门违规申报需求计划，未按规定对拟聘用外部审计力量的数量、人数、专业要求和费用预算等情况进行测算、汇总，擅自夸大需求计划；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）计划管理部门未按规定程序及时对聘用申请计划进行审核、报批，聘用申请计划未经厅（局）长办公会议研究审定即纳入年度审计项目计划，财务管理部门未按规定审核聘请费用即纳入年度审计经费预算，法制、审理部门未制定和报批年度聘用计划，或报批后未及时通知备选成员单位参加现场选取；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）未采取随机产生方式选取参与审计项目的对象，或人为操作故意选取或不选取某个对象；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）未按规定当场宣布和登记选取结果、组织相关人员在选取结果备案书上签字、签订聘用协议和公布选取结果；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第九条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在参与审计工作环节，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未严格把关，参与审计项目的单位选派的外部人员不能胜任工作，或中途擅自更换人员、无故脱岗离岗，未能有效履行协议；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">违规由外部人员担任审计组组长或主审；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">放任或授意由外部人员独立调查取证、私自与被审计单位商谈审计事项、交换处理意见，或以审计机关名义、审计职权和审计成果，为本人、亲属及特定关系人谋取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">未及时对外部人员进行督导和业务复核，不作判断或评估，擅自或借故利用外部人员的专业咨询、专业鉴定或直接将其工作结果作为审计证据；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: transparent;\">（五）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">审计结束后，组长或主审在填报外部审计力量工作情况考评表时，弄虚作假、迁就照顾；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在内部监管环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未将外部人员纳入审计组统一教育、严格管理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">未组织外部人员进行国家审计法律、法规、规章及审计业务培训和审计纪律、职业道德教育，或组织业务培训、廉政教育流于形式；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）接受外部人员的馈赠或回扣，参加由其安排的娱乐活动，向聘请的外部人员提不合理要求，为本人、亲属及特定关系人办理与审计无关事项；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）放任外部人员在聘用期内从事社会兼职工作，或以审计机关名义从事与审计事项无关的活动，或以不正当手段拉拢审计机关人员，故意隐瞒审计发现问题或与被审计单位串通舞弊，从被审计单位获取不正当利益；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）故意泄漏知悉的国家秘密、审计秘密、商业秘密和个人隐私，将取得和形成的审计资料和结论擅自对外披露或者用于与审计无关的目的；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）违规报销因公因私费用，虚报冒领外部审计力量的外勤补助；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）违反审计职业道德规范和审计纪律“八不准”规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十一条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">在经费保障环节，重点防控下列行为：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）未编报或违规编报聘用经费预算；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）未将聘用经费纳入年度经费预算；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）故意或授意挤占、挪用、侵占、套取、调配聘用经费；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（四）将审减额与审计经费直接挂钩，或以业务介绍费、劳务报酬等方式向外部审计力量收取一定比例的费用；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）从外部审计力量的审减收费中留存部分经费，以聘请外部审计力量名义向被审计单位收费，授意或放任其与被审计单位商议所需审计费用，或要求被审计单位直接将审计费用支付给外部审计力量；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）未经考评或考评后未按规定标准支付聘用经费，故意或授意拖延支付聘用经费，从中收受好处；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（七）未执行聘用经费由审计机关支付规定；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（八）其他违反法律法规和廉政规定的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">防控措施</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十二条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">全面排查利用外部审计力量廉政风险，重点排查招标聘用、项目分配、参与审计、内部监管、经费保障、监督制约等方面的风险点，建立利用外部审计力量廉政风险库。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十三条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">修订完善利用外部审计力量廉政责任制，明确监察、法制、审理、计划管理、人事管理、行政管理、财务管理、信息化建设、业务部门等部门（机构）在利用外部审计力量过程中的职责及问责办法，细化工作内容、方法、标准和要求。实行外部审计力量廉政建设情况与职业道德诚信档案、审计项目质量检查评比、目标责任制考核、综合量化考核、聘用费用和工资待遇管理等挂钩机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十四条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">完善利用外部审计力量参与规定范围审计项目的制度规定，以及配套的招标投标管理、资质资格审查、经费管理、综合考核等相关制度机制，明确外部审计力量参与审计工作的条件和范围，细化所需外部审计力量的资质、资格等条件，合理制定经费标准，严格控制、严格审批外部审计力量参与审计工作。积极探索和建立审计业务专家咨询委员会，科学调配和整合审计资源，有效借助外部审计力量对审计项目的技术支持、专业意见和专业鉴定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十五条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格实行利用外部审计力量需求测算、申请审批以及纳入年度项目计划和经费预算管理等制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十六条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">严格执行外部审计力量招投标制度，建立评标专家库和外部审计力量备选库。完善评标专家库随机产生、充实调整等机制。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: red; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十七条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">实行审计项目随机分配制度，采取随机摇号等方式从备选库中选取参与审计项目的外部力量。严格执行合同协议、廉政承诺等管理办</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十八条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">加强外部审计力量的审前业务培训和廉政教育、认同教育，增强国家审计意识和职业道德素养。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第十九条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">认真落实外部人员纳入审计组统一管理的全员责任制，严格执行外部人员不得担任审计组组长和主审、不得单独执行审计业务、严禁委托审计或独立审计等制度规定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">探索建立审计机关与财政、建设、工商、税务等部门和单位的协调沟通机制，实行建立诚信档案、准入退出、社会公示和“黑名单”等制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十一条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立完善利用外部审计力量的审计业务质量、审计职业道德、审计纪律、审计绩效等考核和奖惩办法，认真落实审计组提出考核、使用、付费等意见、建议的规定，业务部门与法制、审理、监察、计划管理、人事管理、财务管理等部门（机构）综合考核机制。探索实行廉政保证金、质量保证金等机制，完善对外部审计力量的责任追究和动态淘汰等机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十二条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">探索建立聘用经费保障机制，推行聘用经费纳入年度政府财政预算、申请项目专项经费、列入项目总预算报批、财政转移支付等方式，多种渠道、规范合理解决所需经费。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第四章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">预警处置</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十三条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">建立审计权力运行风险电子监控系统，将利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控纳入信息化管理，利用</span>OA<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">和</span>AO<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">等平台，采取“制度</span>+<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">科技”的方式，对利用外部审计力量全过程中可能发生的廉政风险，实行流程管理和电子监控。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十四条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">将利用外部审计力量廉政风险信息纳入审计机关廉政风险信息收集机制，充分发挥信息员作用，利用相关工作和活动，多渠道、多方位全面收集风险信息。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十五条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">纪检监察机构（组织）要对收集的风险信息及时进行汇总、分析和评估，根据风险等级、风险类别及预控措施，通过书面函、电子监控系统、手机短信等形式向相关单位和个人发出询问、告知、提示等预警通知，采取谈心疏导、批评教育、信访约谈、诫勉谈话等方式进行风险预警。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十六条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">受到预警的单位和个人，应当及时说明情况、剖析原因，制定和完善整改措施，并反馈处置结果。纪检监察机构（组织）应当加强对预警处置措施落实情况的监督，对整改不及时、落实不到位的，应根据有关规定实行问责或组织处理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第五章</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">附</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十七条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各级审计机关应将利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控工作纳入党风廉政建设责任制检查和目标考核内容，建立利用外部审计力量廉政风险防控工作考核制度，加强工作指导、督促、检查和考核，对不认真落实防控措施的单位和个人按有关规定实施责任追究。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十八条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">各级审计机关应结合本办法制定具体实施细则和相关配套制度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第二十九条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法由驻湖北省审计厅纪检组负责解释。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">第三十条</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">本办法自发布之日起施行。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-12-30 16:16:44', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 16:16:44', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 16:31:36', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
