t-indent: 41px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 35px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">中共湖北省审计厅党组</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 35px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 276px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2013年5月20日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; background: transparent;\">湖北省审计机关建立健全惩治和预防</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; background: transparent;\">腐败体系2013—2017年工作细则</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; background: transparent;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">为认真落实中共中央关于《建立健全惩治和预防腐败体系2013—2017年工作规划》（以下简称《工作规划》）和湖北省委《关于贯彻落实〈建立健全惩治和预防腐败体系2013—2017年工作规划〉实施办法》、《审计署党组关于贯彻落实〈建立健全惩治和预防腐败体系2013—2017年工作规划〉的实施办法》（以下简称两个《实施办法》），扎实推进全省审计机关惩治和预防腐败体系（以下简称惩防体系）建设，制定本工作细则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 29px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">一、指导思想</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">以邓小平理论、“三个代表”重要思想、科学发展观为指导，深入贯彻落实党的十八大、十八届三中全会和习近平总书记系列重要讲话精神，按照中央和省委统一部署和要求，坚持标本兼治、综合治理、惩防并举、注重预防，强化对权力运行的监督制约，加强党的作风建设，科学有效预防腐败，以零容忍态度坚决惩治腐败，将惩防体系建设更好地融入审计工作各个环节，不断提高惩防体系建设科学化水平。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">二、工作目标</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">到2017年，使全省审计机关党风廉政建设深入推进，“四风”问题得到有效治理，审计廉政权力制约和监督体系更加完善，审计干部队伍建设呈现新的风貌，为全面完成审计工作任务、促进湖北审计工作转型升级提供有力保障。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">三、主要内容</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（一）坚持不懈抓实党的作风建设。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．持之以恒贯彻落实中央“八项规定”精神。要贯彻落实中央“八项规定”、省委“六条意见”和审计署“十八条意见”精神，认真执行厅党组改进审计工作作风、密切联系群众的32条措施，深入开展“三抓一促”、“三短一简一俭”活动；坚持从领导做起、从自我做起、从点滴做起，由浅入深，循序渐进，防止和纠正打折扣、搞变通行为，严肃查处违纪违规行为。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：人事处、机关党委、办公室、监察室）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．着力健全改进作风常态化机制。巩固群众路线教育实践活动成果，围绕纠正“四风”，健全领导干部改进作风、深入基层、联系群众制度机制；健全规范“三公经费”和会议费管理等规章制度；健全厉行节约、反对浪费方面制度办法；进一步加强日常管理监督，强化制度刚性运行，不断提升制度执行力。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：人事处、办公室）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．加强纪律建设。采取多种措施学习、贯彻、维护党章，使每位党员牢固树立党的意识和组织纪律观念。严格遵守政治纪律，坚决维护以习近平同志为总书记的党中央集体领导权威；严格遵守组织纪律，坚决做到“四个服从”；严格遵守廉政纪律，杜绝各种不廉洁行为和违纪违规问题；严格遵守保密纪律，预防各种失密泄密问题发生；严格遵守财经纪律，严控“三公经费”、会议费开支，纠正大手大脚、铺张浪费等现象；严格遵守工作纪律，坚决防止假公济私、以审谋私等问题发生。强化执纪检查，确保纪律刚性约束，使纪律真正成为带电的高压线，着力打造审计铁军。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：机关党委、人事处、办公室、监察室）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（二）完善反腐倡廉教育体系。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．深化理想信念教育。把理想信念、党性宗旨教育和审计人员核心价值观教育，作为党员领导干部培训、党员和入党积极分子培训的重要内容，采取多种形式抓好落实，进一步坚定“三个自信”，牢固树立正确的世界观、人生观和价值观，打牢反腐倡廉思想基础。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：人事处、机关党委）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．打造反腐倡廉“教育链”。以处以上党员干部为重点，将党风党纪、廉洁从政、廉洁自律等内容纳入中心组和各支部学习计划，安排专门时间抓好专题学习；以党风廉政建设“宣教月”为载体，经常开展内容丰富、形式多样、特色鲜明的廉政教育活动；以审计组为重点，扎实抓好审前廉政谈话、审中廉政提醒、审后廉政讲评等教育工作。注重树立和宣传勤政廉政先进典型，开展廉洁从政示范教育；坚持抓早抓小，加强对苗头性、倾向性问题的日常提醒；坚持每季度开展一次警示教育，充分发挥违纪违规违法案例的警示作用；充分运用干部在线学习、远程教育、网上测评等方式开展经常性的岗位廉政教育。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：机关党委、人事处、监察室、法规处）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">6</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．推进廉政文化建设。将党风廉政建设和反腐败工作纳入宣传教育工作总体部署和年度安排，充分各种媒体，及时宣传全省审计机关学习贯彻党的反腐倡廉理论和方针政策有关情况，大力推广各单位在反腐倡廉建设中的创新举措和典型经验。把培养廉洁价值理念融入审计机关精神文明建设和法制教育之中，推动廉政文化内容、形式和传播手段创新。制定湖北省审计机关廉政文化建设示范单位评选标准，在全系统开展创建“廉政文化建设示范单位”活动，打造具有审计特色和单位特点的廉政文化品牌。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：机关党委、监察室、综合处、办公室）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（三）健全反腐倡廉法规制度体系。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37p