-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（五）坚决查办违纪违法案件。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">16</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．加大信访监督工作力度。利用多种渠道和方式，为群众表达诉求、反映问题、提出意见建议、查询办理结果搭建平台；进一步规范信访事项受理、交办、督办、回复等工作程序，增强信访工作实效性。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：办公室、综合处、各业务处、机关党委、监察室）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">17</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．坚持抓早抓小，防微杜渐。及时掌握党员干部的思想动态和工作生活情况，对苗头性、倾向性问题，早发现、早报告、早处置。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：人事处、监察室、机关党委）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">18</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．加大对违纪违规问题的惩治力度，发挥案件查办的惩戒警示功能。严肃查处以审谋私、权钱交易、失职渎职等行为，及时通报审计干部违纪违法案件，发挥案例的警示教育功能。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：监察室、机关党委、人事处、法规处）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（六）有效发挥审计监督在反腐败中的尖兵和利剑作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">19</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．加强对中央“八项规定”和省委“六条意见”精神贯彻执行情况的审计监督。把各级政府、部门及领导干部贯彻落实中央“八项规定”和省委“六条意见”精神执行情况，执行厉行勤俭节约相关要求的情况，作为审计监督的重点内容，重点关注“三公”经费、会议费、培训费、楼堂馆所建设、内部接待场所等情况，促进中央和省委相关要求的贯彻落实，促进建设俭朴政府。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：各业务处、经责局）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">20</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．深化经济责任审计工作。深化对党政主要领导干部和国有企业领导人员的经济责任审计，全面落实《湖北省领导干部经济责任问责暂行办法》，推动健全有权必有责、用权受监督、失职要问责、违法要追究的监督机制。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：经责局）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">21</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．加大对经济领域重大违法违纪问题的揭示力度。坚持反腐倡廉与改革发展“力度统一论”，紧紧盯住财政资金管理、公共工程建设、银行贷款发放、土地和矿产资源出让转让、国有资产处置和国有企业投资经营等重点环节，对审计发现的重大问题和案件线索，要锲而不舍地一查到底，充分发挥审计反腐“尖兵”和“利剑”作用。认真办理、及时移送审计发现的案件线索，扩大审计效果，促进反腐倡廉建设。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">（责任单位：各业务处、经责局，法规处）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\">四、工作措施</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">22</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．强化责任意识。厅党组对党风廉政建设负主体责任，纪检监察机构负监督责任。要把推进惩防体系建设作为一项重要政治任务来抓，把贯彻落实本细则列入厅党组重要议事日程，融入审计业务工作、审计法规体系建设、干部队伍建设和审计文化建设，做到同部署、同落实、同检查。厅党组书记要履行第一责任人职责，党组其他成员要按照分工抓好分管处室相关工作，处室主要负责人要履行“一岗双责”责任，增强抓好党风廉政建设的自觉性和主动性。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">23</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．增强工作合力。各责任单位要加强组织领导，各项任务涉及到的其他单位要积极配合。责任单位主要负责人要组织提出具体措施，认真落实所担负的工作任务。厅党风廉政建设领导小组办公室、机关党委（纪委）要充分发挥监督检查作用，对工作落实不力、造成不良后果的，严肃追究领导责任。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 黑体; background: transparent;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 37px; color: rgb(78, 76, 76); font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; text-indent: 43px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">24</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; background: transparent;\">．狠抓任务落实。抓好惩防体系建设责任分解和任务分工，有重点、分步骤地落实本细则部署的任务。对阶段性任务，要在规定时间内高质量完成；对持续性工作，要结合新情况新问题推进提高。建立工作台账制度，按要求及时报送工作信息。各单位要把贯彻落实本细则与落实党风廉政建设责任制考核结合起来，列入领导班子和领导干部考核评价范围，作为工作实绩评定的重要内容，确保各项任务落到实处。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-12-30 16:17:11', null, '1', '0', '1', '2015-12-30 16:17:11', null, '', '1', null, null, '1', '1', '2015-12-30 16:31:28', '', '402881fd515b4f9b01515b5a5b620007', '1', '0', null, null, '20130419093149037845634429844034', '0', '', 'NULL', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2', null);
