;background: transparent\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background: transparent\">审计组在实施审计前，应当将有关审计事项和审计纪律全面、真实地告知被审计单位，主动接受被审计单位监督。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;background: transparent\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 黑体;background: transparent\">第三条</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;background: transparent\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background: transparent\">审计告知的内容包括：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;background: transparent\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;background: transparent\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background: transparent\">（一）审计项目名称；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 37px;color: rgb(78, 76, 76);font-family: Simsun;white-space: normal;background: rgb(249, 249, 249)\"><span style=\";padding: 