riant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 27.2px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 23.4pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;;font-family:宋体\">经调查核实，你公司存在以下环境违法行为：</span></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 27.2px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 23.4pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;;font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12pt;\">、车间部分生产废水及污水收集管道溢流废水进入雨水排口排入外环境；</span></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 27.2px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: 23.4pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;;font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all !important; word-wrap: break-word !imp